00:14:52.227 --> 00:14:53.409
the next electron?
 

00:14:53.409 --> 00:14:53.519
Zack?
 

00:14:53.519 --> 00:14:54.178
Student:  Oxygen.
 

00:14:54.178 --> 00:14:57.557
Prof: To the oxygen,
because that's the next highest

00:14:57.557 --> 00:14:59.129
