00:16:06.480 --> 00:16:08.573
So we can look at what's
interesting, the valence

00:16:08.573 --> 00:16:11.278
orbitals, the ones that are
going to be involved in bonding;

00:16:11.278 --> 00:16:13.860
these don't have anything to do
