00:16:13.860 --> 00:16:15.879
Okay, so there's the first one.
 

00:16:15.879 --> 00:16:19.210
Russell, tell me something
about the shape of this?

00:16:19.210 --> 00:16:20.509
Does it surprise you?
 

00:16:20.509 --> 00:16:21.437
Student:  No.
 

00:16:21.437 --> 00:16:23.480
It's highly distorted towards
